snippet.description:
Episode 2: Baalveer Kasam Kaal
---------------------------------------
When Himbaash Lok's evil fairy, Aageel attacks his mother, Baalveer saves her. It was later revealed that Udaaka Lok's chief Maha Mahi Uttaan was testing Baalveer's abilities. Everyone admires Baalveer's strength and how he dealt with Aageel. Meanwhile, Himbaash Lok's fairy, Aageel brags about her extraordinary magical abilities, known as "Maha Jadu," with which she is now capable of defeating the ultimate hero, Baalveer. Maha Mahi Mutaan of Udaaka Lok warns Baalveer about his impending arrival and advises him to cut ties with his mother. Why was Baalveer given such dire warnings? How will Baalveer defeat Udaaka Lok's new nemesis? Keep an eye out!

Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com
